HealthModel --> MongoDB
FieldModel --> MongoDB
PropertyModel --> MongoDB
DetectionModel --> MongoDB
ProfileModel --> MongoDB

Business --> MLService : API Calls
Devices --> API : Heartbeat
Cameras --> MLService : Image/Video
MLService --> Business : Detection Results

@enduml

